---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = 'June 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Life Momentum Score is private by design. All your habit data stays on your device — no accounts, no logins, no tracking, no servers."
>
  <article class="container-page py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-mute">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-body">
        Life Momentum Score is built to be private by default. The short version: your data
        belongs to you, it stays on your device, and we never see it.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-10">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Your data stays on your device</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            Every habit you log is saved locally in your own browser using a built-in technology
            called localStorage. It never leaves your device, and it is never uploaded to any
            server. If you clear your browser data, your history is cleared with it — so the data
            lives entirely under your control.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">No account, no login</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            You don't create an account to use Life Momentum Score. There is no sign-up, no
            password, and no profile. You can start tracking immediately without giving us anything.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">No personal information collected</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            We do not ask for, collect, or store your name, email address, location, or any other
            personal details. Because there are no accounts and no servers, there is simply nothing
            for us to gather about you.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">No analytics, no advertising</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            At this time, Life Momentum Score uses no analytics tools and shows no advertising. We
            do not track your behavior across the web, and there are no third-party trackers
            embedded in the experience.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            As the product grows, this policy may be updated — for example, if we ever introduce
            optional analytics or advertising. If that happens, we will revise this page and update
            the date above. Any future change will be explained in the same plain language you see
            here.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Questions</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            If anything here is unclear, reach out any time at
            <a href="/contact" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-ink">our contact page</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary inline-flex">Start Tracking</a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary inline-flex">Why we built this</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
